node.text: its always been a childhood dream of mine to be on the cover of @altpress this is like getting rolling stone for me growing up as a poor awkward emo kid. dreams rly do come tru u just gotta push thru the pain long enough to watch them happen. I had to leave this shoot early cause i was having a pancreatitis flare up and was throwing up but i showed up and smiled thru the pain cause i knew this shoot would inspire someone somewhere. misery lake ep is out today the link is in my bio 🏃‍♂️ life is war
